df = pd.read_csv('./data/data_filled.csv', index_col=0)
df = df.drop(['시가총액', '기업명'], axis=1)

encoder = LabelEncoder()
df['업종코드'] = encoder.fit_transform(df['업종코드'])
df['업종코드'] = df['업종코드'].astype(np.object)
